d">Time differences in Japanese vs. U.S. versions</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VTdLrPOTAkFDJSw9MuPktmxE6y9eVuFUkUOhuSpM7lY">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/ ... UOhuSpM7lY</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Gameshark code/Siglemic fan site (xd):</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://siglemic.net/resources" target="_blank">http://siglemic.net/resources</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Harper's (LOL) GS/VC Codes(reset level, death code, etc.):</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://pastebin.com/MCNtx2K3" target="_blank">http://pastebin.com/MCNtx2K3</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">SM64 Course Information:</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.sm64.com/" target="_blank">http://www.sm64.com/</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">More MAREO information~~</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://sm64.org/" target="_blank">http://sm64.org/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Will add more onto this post later! Hope this helps some people out!  <img src="http://marioruns.com/forum/images/smilies/sausage.png" alt="Sausage" title="Sausage" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=58">MiracleTea</a> — 22 Apr 2014, 03:42</p><hr />
